rows.label: bf08430100_0010
rows.name: You know you can't control it.

rows.label: bf08430100_0020
rows.name:
I hear you've been apointed...
as the Cardinal's assistant.

rows.label: bf08430100_0040
rows.name:
Hmph.
Just thought I'd come and say goodbye.

rows.label: bf08430100_0050
rows.name: Would you rather I leave without saying anything?

rows.label: bf08430100_0060
rows.name:
"Goodbye"?!
What would compel you to leave me?

rows.label: bf08430100_0080
rows.name: I can use all my power, even if I'm alone.

rows.label: bf08430100_0085
rows.name: I'll keep existing even if you die.

rows.label: bf08430100_0100
rows.name:
The Holy See, the believers...I despise them all.
Humans are a waste for this world, but they still have use.

rows.label: bf08430100_0110
rows.name: So...I thought I'd give you what you wished for.

rows.label: bf08430100_0140
rows.name:
Isn't that why you sought the supreme existence, God.
And climbed the World Tree?

rows.label: bf08430100_0170
rows.name:
There must be someone out there
who can use this core...
